      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>GERSUNY--Conrad, 75, at Morrisville, VT. Jeweler, sculpture, owner of McDougal Street's Conrad Shop. Gentle, generous, gifted, loquacious. Survived by brother Carl and family, three exwives who remain his friends, his long time devoted partner, Portia Arthur and his beloved cat, Sheena. Social Justice was his religion.</p>
